<section>
  <title>Parameter Widget</title>
  <para id="parameterwidget"><informalexample>
      <variablelist>
        <varlistentry>
          <term>Filter</term>
          <listitem>
            <para>Select a filter from the list of available filters, then
            select the QUERY button to generate search results. To learn more
            about working with search filters, please see <xref
            linkend="introSearchFilters" />.</para>
          </listitem>
        </varlistentry>
        <varlistentry>
          <term>MORE</term>
          <listitem>
            <para>Select this button to show the parameters underlying the
            saved filter. To hide the parameters, simply click the MORE button
            a second time.</para>
          </listitem>
        </varlistentry>
        <varlistentry>
          <term>Search</term>
          <listitem>
            <para>When building a query, you have the following
            options:</para>
            <variablelist>
              <varlistentry>
                <term>+</term>
                <listitem>
                  <para>Select to add new parameters to the query.</para>
                </listitem>
              </varlistentry>
              <varlistentry>
                <term>-</term>
                <listitem>
                  <para>Select to remove parameters from the query.</para>
                </listitem>
              </varlistentry>
              <varlistentry>
                <term>SAVE</term>
                <listitem>
                  <para>Select to save your filter for future use.</para>
                </listitem>
              </varlistentry>
              <varlistentry>
                <term>MANAGE</term>
                <listitem>
                  <para>Select this button to manage your saved
                  filters.</para>
                </listitem>
              </varlistentry>
            </variablelist>
          </listitem>
        </varlistentry>
      </variablelist>
    </informalexample></para>
</section>
